You may be interested in an article in one of the Crypto annuals by Michael
fellows and Neal Koblitz entitled "Kid Crypto" about crypto ideas and protocols
accessible to kids.  I thaink it was in the 1992 or 1993 annual, starts on page
371 and runs about twenty pages.
 
